sentences.sContent: Could you get rid of some of that clutter in your bedroom?
sentences.sCn: 你能把你卧室那些杂物清理掉一些吗？

remMethod.val: 人们为了抢购黄油 (butter)， 场面一片混乱 (clutter)

trans.tranOther: a large number of things that are scattered somewhere in an untidy way
to cover or fill a space or room with too many things, so that it looks very untidy
